-[panting]

2
00:00:14,041 --> 00:00:16,000
-[grunts]
-[energy surging]

3
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:19,750
Hello there, Visitor!
Thank you for saving us!

4
00:00:19,833 --> 00:00:21,750
Wait.
So, you’re okay?

5
00:00:21,833 --> 00:00:24,083
The Star Children are always
automatically protected

6
00:00:24,166 --> 00:00:25,791
by holy Matryoshka dolls

7
00:00:25,875 --> 00:00:27,750
when they’re in
any kind of danger.

8
00:00:27,833 --> 00:00:30,041
Yep! So, you don’t
have to worry about us!

9
00:00:30,125 --> 00:00:31,375
That’s incredible.

10
00:00:31,458 --> 00:00:32,916
But what about your wounds?

11
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:34,750
Are you saying that
you’re fully recovered?

12
00:00:34,833 --> 00:00:36,833
Right!
We’re both as good as new!

13
00:00:36,916 --> 00:00:38,375
I’m glad to hear it!

14
00:00:38,458 --> 00:00:40,416
You stand no chance
against them right now!

15
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:42,750
Back to the foster home
for more training!

16
00:00:42,833 --> 00:00:44,208
[VIRGO, CANCER]
Got it!

17
00:00:44,291 --> 00:00:46,875
Itsuki, you must defeat
the Impurities next time.

18
00:00:46,958 --> 00:00:49,083
Yeah, I know.
Apart from everything else,

19
00:00:49,166 --> 00:00:51,666
I can’t stand seeing the Star
Children suffer like that.

20
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:53,250
So, let’s try again!

21
00:00:53,333 --> 00:00:55,791
Yes, honored Visitor!

22
00:00:55,875 --> 00:00:57,333
Itsuki is beginning to develop

23
