of duty as a Visitor.

24
00:01:00,041 --> 00:01:01,375
[giggles]

25
00:01:01,458 --> 00:01:03,125
All that’s left is to improve
his technique

26
00:01:03,208 --> 00:01:05,166
for the all-important
Love Ritual!

27
00:01:05,250 --> 00:01:07,208
After all, he was a total newbie
at sexytime stuff

28
00:01:07,291 --> 00:01:08,666
’til just a few days ago.

29
00:01:08,750 --> 00:01:10,416
So he could use a little help
with his [barking]

30
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:12,125
in their [meowing] and I’m
just the one to do it,

31
00:01:12,208 --> 00:01:13,500
if I don’t say so myself.

32
00:01:13,583 --> 00:01:15,875
[VIRGO, CANCER]
Help us, Visitor!

33
00:01:15,958 --> 00:01:17,708
They’re way too strong!

34
00:01:17,791 --> 00:01:20,125
Wow, already?
That's rough.

35
00:01:20,208 --> 00:01:23,000
This isn’t good.
We can’t even get close to them.

36
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:25,375
We gotta have more training.

37
00:01:25,458 --> 00:01:27,208
Don’t you get it?
This is weird!

38
00:01:27,291 --> 00:01:29,166
Something’s really wrong,
Narcisstes!

39
00:01:29,250 --> 00:01:30,708
[NARCISSTES]
Okay, calm down, Mana.

40
00:01:30,791 --> 00:01:32,291
A typical Visitor
would’ve defeated

41
00:01:32,375 --> 00:01:33,958
an Impurity Lord by now!

42
00:01:34,041 --> 00:01:36,375
But he still can’t even seem
to beat a single minion!

43
00:01:36,458 --> 00:01:37,625
[ITSUKI]
I’m sorry.

44
00:01:37,708 --> 00:01:39,583
I know it has to be
my fault, somehow.

45
00:01:40,666 --> 00:01:43,458
Hey, are you even listening?

46
00:01:43,541 --> 00:01:45,333
