47
00:01:45,416 --> 00:01:47,208
The maidens of the twelve
constellations

48
00:01:47,291 --> 00:01:50,208
have never all changed at once
in our entire history.

49
00:01:50,291 --> 00:01:52,291
So, what’re you trying
to say is--

50
00:01:52,375 --> 00:01:54,708
I’m saying that we’re in a real
state of emergency.

51
00:01:54,791 --> 00:01:56,791
So, that’s it?
There’s no possible way

52
00:01:56,875 --> 00:01:58,625
for me to defeat the Impurities?

53
00:01:58,708 --> 00:02:00,208
That’s not what I said.

54
00:02:00,291 --> 00:02:03,125
Our academics know what to do
thanks to ancient texts.

55
00:02:03,208 --> 00:02:04,875
Though such writings
are often disregarded

56
00:02:04,958 --> 00:02:06,291
as being stories
and legends.

57
00:02:06,375 --> 00:02:07,541
Don’t tell me.

58
00:02:07,625 --> 00:02:08,875
Do you mean... ?

59
00:02:08,958 --> 00:02:10,875
Itsuki, listen well, now.

60
00:02:10,958 --> 00:02:12,791
If we’re to get through
this crisis,

61
00:02:12,875 --> 00:02:15,583
you have no choice but to
perform a Double Love Ritual.

62
00:03:48,250 --> 00:03:50,708
[ITSUKI] Um, what's a
Double Love Ritual?

63
00:03:50,791 --> 00:03:52,250
[giggling]

64
00:03:52,333 --> 00:03:53,958
I bet you already know!

65
00:03:54,041 --> 00:03:56,583
It’s a ritual where you have
two sexual partners at once!

66
00:03:56,666 --> 00:03:57,916
Sounds fun, right?

67
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,541
You obviously need
a lot of stamina

68
00:03:59,625 --> 00:04:01,500
for this particular ceremony,
but if you can swing it,

69
00:04:01,583 --> 00:04:03,500
it’s a practical buffet
for the senses!

70
00:04:03,583 --> 00:04:05,208
A feast for your whole body!

71
00:04:05,291 --> 00:04:06,666
Two arms and legs
may not feel like enough,

72
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,125
but remember,
you can always activate

73
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:09,958
Little Itsuki in the middle,
you pervert, you!

74
00:04:10,041 --> 00:04:11,125
I don’t think I understand.

75
00:04:11,208 --> 00:04:12,333
Fool!
It’s a three[bleep]!

76
00:04:12,416 --> 00:04:13,833
A three[bleep]!

77
00:04:13,916 --> 00:04:15,416
Would you grow a pair
and stop playing dumb?

78
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,958
I’ll put it as simply
as I possibly can:

79
00:04:17,041 --> 00:04:18,500
it’s a lovey-dovey activity

80
00:04:18,583 --> 00:04:20,416
performed by a group
of men and women.

81
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,750
Come on, you know you
wanna try it, right?

82
00:04:22,833 --> 00:04:25,333
