a group activity, yeah.

83
00:04:25,416 --> 00:04:27,416
You’re such a
good little pervert.

84
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:29,416
By the way, you can use these.

85
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:30,958
Believe me, this’ll be heaven.

86
00:04:31,041 --> 00:04:32,583
Group cooperative play
that’s two times better

87
00:04:32,666 --> 00:04:34,875
than sixty-nining.
A brand new thing!

88
00:04:34,958 --> 00:04:36,666
That’s a little intimidating.

89
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:39,083
Don’t worry about a thing!
The Visitor can relax

90
00:04:39,166 --> 00:04:40,625
and leave everything
to the maidens!

91
00:04:40,708 --> 00:04:43,208
You know, it’s, what do you
call it? In Sola.

92
00:04:43,291 --> 00:04:45,250
Oh, you know, the fish
that’s popular for sushi!

93
00:04:45,333 --> 00:04:47,291
Are you talking
about tuna, my fave?

94
00:04:47,375 --> 00:04:48,666
[MANA]
Yes! That! Tuna!

95
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,875
All you need to do
is be present and relax

96
00:04:50,958 --> 00:04:53,083
and focus all of your attention
on one spot.

97
00:04:53,166 --> 00:04:54,791
Just lay there like a dead fish

98
00:04:54,875 --> 00:04:57,541
and the two maidens will happily
tussle and cook you right up!

99
00:04:59,250 --> 00:05:00,750
[NARCISSTES]
According to the ancient texts,

100
00:05:00,833 --> 00:05:02,583
the Star Children
who are born as a product

101
00:05:02,666 --> 00:05:05,000
of the Double Love Ritual
are even more remarkable.

102
00:05:05,083 --> 00:05:07,666
Supposedly, even stronger than
the ones you’ve already made.

103
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:09,458
Why, "supposedly?"

104
00:05:09,541 --> 00:05:11,416
[NARCISSTES] For at least
the past few hundred years,

105
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:14,125
a Visitor capable of bonding
with multiple maidens at once

106
00:05:14,208 --> 00:05:16,666
was not thought
to actually exist.

107
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:19,541
In other words, the Double Love
Ritual is uncharted territory,

108
00:05:19,625 --> 00:05:21,000
even for us.

109
00:05:21,083 --> 00:05:22,708
[ITSUKI]
No pressure, then.

110
00:05:22,791 --> 00:05:24,916
On top of that, we really have
no way of knowing

111
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,166
what kind of damage
this could do to your body.

112
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:29,666
A Visitor’s bond with a maiden
is very intense.

113
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:31,250
Well, is there any other way?

114
00:05:31,333 --> 00:05:33,666
[NARCISSTES] I’m sorry.
We can't find a better path

115
00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:35,375
to defeating
the Impurities right now.

116
00:05:35,458 --> 00:05:37,791
Just think about it:
the lucky Visitor with the duty

117
00:05:37,875 --> 00:05:39,458
to bond intimately
with the beautiful maidens

118
00:05:39,541 --> 00:05:41,333
of the twelve
constellations is you!

119
00:05:41,416 --> 00:05:42,541
Isn’t that amazing?

120
00:05:42,625 --> 00:05:43,875
Don’t you feel like
the luckiest?

121
00:05:43,958 --> 00:05:45,458
You should be proud,
you’ll be a pioneer

122
00:05:45,541 --> 00:05:47,666
exploring bold new frontiers!

123
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:51,125
Just give me
a minute to process.

124
00:05:51,208 --> 00:05:53,041
[MAHIRU]
I wish Mana knew how not subtle

125
