this outing actually is.

126
00:05:54,958 --> 00:05:56,958
We have hot springs
in Granvania,

127
00:05:57,041 --> 00:05:58,500
just like you do in Sola!

128
00:05:58,583 --> 00:06:00,500
It’ll be a great chance
for you both to relax

129
00:06:00,583 --> 00:06:02,791
and get some much
needed R and R.

130
00:06:02,875 --> 00:06:05,000
Not to mention, doing it under
the big, open sky

131
00:06:05,083 --> 00:06:06,333
is liberating as heck!

132
00:06:06,416 --> 00:06:07,583
The only real drawback is,

133
00:06:07,666 --> 00:06:09,041
you might totally
wear yourselves out

134
00:06:09,125 --> 00:06:11,125
and be even more exhausted
when you get back!

135
00:06:11,208 --> 00:06:12,750
[laughs]

136
00:06:12,833 --> 00:06:15,500
Yeah, it’s pretty obvious
he’s up to something again.

137
00:06:15,583 --> 00:06:16,791
What do you mean, "again?"

138
00:06:16,875 --> 00:06:18,333
Well, there’s
this Double Love Ritual

139
00:06:18,416 --> 00:06:20,750
he wants me to do-- Oh!

140
00:06:20,833 --> 00:06:23,666
Oh, don’t stop now.
A Double Love Ritual, huh?

141
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:25,875
Yeah. Never mind.

142
00:06:25,958 --> 00:06:29,708
Itsuki, you really are one
of the most frustrating people--

143
00:06:29,791 --> 00:06:31,166
-[shouts]
-[ITSUKI grunts]

144
00:06:32,166 --> 00:06:34,416
Don’t worry,
I’ll grab your bag.

145
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,625
What is this?

146
00:06:35,708 --> 00:06:37,791
He’s not lookin’
very good, is he?

147
00:06:37,875 --> 00:06:40,000
Hey! That’s private!

148
00:06:40,083 --> 00:06:42,250
Wait, is that thing
what I think it is?

149
00:06:42,333 --> 00:06:43,875
Don’t get any stupid ideas!

150
00:06:43,958 --> 00:06:45,625
I’m just keeping it
because it’s cute.

151
00:06:45,708 --> 00:06:47,708
It has nothing to do with
the fact that you gave it to me

152
00:06:47,791 --> 00:06:50,125
so get that out of your head!

153
00:06:50,208 --> 00:06:54,250
Wow! I’ve never been to a hot
spring quite like this before!

154
00:06:54,333 --> 00:06:56,000
[ITSUKI] It looks like
there’s only one spring.

155
00:06:56,083 --> 00:06:58,500
[MAHIRU] Who cares?
We’ll go in together.

156
00:06:58,583 --> 00:07:00,833
We used to take baths
together all the time.

157
00:07:00,916 --> 00:07:02,083
Yeah, same same.

158
00:07:02,166 --> 00:07:03,458
Are you kidding me right now?

159
00:07:03,541 --> 00:07:05,500
We were, like,
five years old then!

160
00:07:05,583 --> 00:07:08,458
Stop freaking out.
I’m getting in, so deal with it.

161
00:07:08,541 --> 00:07:10,833
Mahiru, come on!
Cut it out!

162
00:07:18,916 --> 00:07:21,541
Would you please get your dirty
mind out of the gutter?

163
00:07:21,625 --> 00:07:24,166
I came totally prepared
for something like this.

164
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:31,375
It’s so good.
Feels like I’m about to melt.

165
00:07:31,458 --> 00:07:33,291
Itsuki, aren’t you gonna get in?

166
00:07:35,083 --> 00:07:37,250
Why are you making
such a huge deal about this?

167
00:07:37,333 --> 00:07:39,000
Just take ’em off, already!

168
00:07:39,083 --> 00:07:40,833
Just don’t look, okay?

169
00:07:40,916 --> 00:07:43,708
'Course not.
I’m not the perv around here.

170
00:07:44,833 --> 00:07:47,250
[ITSUKI] Wow.
This place really is wonderful.

171
00:07:47,333 --> 00:07:50,000
Although, it does
sting a little bit.

172
00:07:51,833 --> 00:07:53,041
What’s wrong?

173
00:07:53,125 --> 00:07:54,333
[MAHIRU]
That mark.

174
00:07:54,416 --> 00:07:55,666
[ITSUKI]
Oh, sorry.

175
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:57,791
Is there dirt on me
or something?

176
00:07:57,875 --> 00:07:59,125
No, it’s not that.

177
00:07:59,208 --> 00:08:00,958
Why do you have
so many injuries?

178
00:08:02,250 --> 00:08:03,750
[ITSUKI]
I guess from training.

179
00:08:03,833 --> 00:08:06,208
It feels like I’ve leveled up
kind of a lot.

180
00:08:06,291 --> 00:08:08,541
Still not strong enough to beat
Impurities, though.

181
00:08:08,625 --> 00:08:11,291
So, you’ll make more, then.
Star Children.

182
00:08:11,375 --> 00:08:13,125
Yes, of course.

183
00:08:13,208 --> 00:08:14,916
I have to try.

184
00:08:16,083 --> 00:08:17,875
What’s wrong, Mahiru?

185
00:08:17,958 --> 00:08:20,041
Hey.
You in there?

186
00:08:20,125 --> 00:08:21,458
Listen well, warrior.

187
00:08:21,541 --> 00:08:22,875
The battles may
be getting tough,

188
00:08:22,958 --> 00:08:25,041
but you are not to die,
understand?

189
00:08:25,125 --> 00:08:26,708
All of a sudden,
you’re concerned?

190
00:08:26,791 --> 00:08:28,125
Shut up and listen to me!

191
00:08:28,208 --> 00:08:30,458
I’m just saying
that you mustn’t die!

192
00:08:30,541 --> 00:08:32,750
I get it. I’ll do my best
not to die

193
00:08:32,833 --> 00:08:34,333
’til I can get you back home.

194
00:08:34,416 --> 00:08:35,791
So is that a promise?

195
00:08:35,875 --> 00:08:37,333
Come on, don’t worry.

196
00:08:37,416 --> 00:08:39,875
The Star Children and I
are always getting stronger.

197
00:08:39,958 --> 00:08:41,833
Next time, we’ll
beat the Impurities.

198
00:08:41,916 --> 00:08:44,833
Despite how she may look,
Mahiru is really a huge crybaby,

199
00:08:44,916 --> 00:08:46,875
so you should probably
keep protecting her.

200
00:08:46,958 --> 00:08:48,958
Don’t worry,
I definitely plan to,

201
00:08:49,041 --> 00:08:51,708
but Mahiru
isn’t really a crybaby, is she?

202
00:08:52,833 --> 00:08:54,083
Yeah, it’s weird.

203
00:08:54,166 --> 00:08:56,416
It’s not like me
to be insecure, is it?

204
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:58,541
But suddenly, here we are
in this strange place

205
00:08:58,625 --> 00:08:59,875
and they’re telling us

206
00:08:59,958 --> 00:09:02,416
we’ve been chosen
as Visitor and maiden.

207
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:04,541
And I really can’t believe
that just a few days ago

208
00:09:04,625 --> 00:09:06,708
we were in a love ritual.

209
00:09:08,083 --> 00:09:09,958
-[whimpering]
-[splashing]

210
00:09:11,541 --> 00:09:13,125
[ITSUKI]
Hey, where’d you go?

211
00:09:16,833 --> 00:09:19,333
Oh, my gosh.
What happened to me?

212
00:09:19,416 --> 00:09:21,708
Passed out from the heat.
You okay?

213
00:09:21,791 --> 00:09:23,583
How ya feeling?

214
00:09:24,541 --> 00:09:27,208
[MAHIRU] Wow.
I’m sorry I’ve been such a pain.

215
00:09:27,291 --> 00:09:28,541
[ITSUIKI]
You haven't.

216
00:09:28,625 --> 00:09:29,958
It’s getting kind of
chilly, though.

217
00:09:30,041 --> 00:09:31,708
We should head back.

218
00:09:31,791 --> 00:09:33,291
[MAHIRU]
Okay, let’s go.

219
00:09:34,458 --> 00:09:36,000
Wait, where’s my key chain?

220
00:09:36,083 --> 00:09:38,791
Oh, sorry. I think I was just
so focused on trying

221
00:09:38,875 --> 00:09:40,583
to save you
that I forgot about it.

222
00:09:40,666 --> 00:09:43,000
I’m sure it’s down in the bottom
of the hot spring.

223
00:09:43,083 --> 00:09:46,000
Oh, my gosh, it can’t
be gone. It can't.

224
00:09:46,083 --> 00:09:47,625
Hey, what are you doing?

225
00:09:47,708 --> 00:09:50,958
-[splashing]
-[MAHIRU] It’s freezing!

226
00:09:53,416 --> 00:09:55,375
[ITSUKI] I heard this hot spring
turns into cold water

227
00:09:55,458 --> 00:09:58,000
after sunset.
Why don’t you go get changed?

228
00:09:58,083 --> 00:09:59,458
I’ll wait for you.

229
00:09:59,541 --> 00:10:01,166
You’re the Visitor and the fate
of this world

230
00:10:01,250 --> 00:10:02,791
literally rests in your hands.

231
00:10:02,875 --> 00:10:05,000
I can’t let you catch
a cold or anything!

232
00:10:05,083 --> 00:10:07,375
Don’t worry.
Wait here, okay?

233
00:10:09,166 --> 00:10:10,458
’Kay.

234
00:10:13,875 --> 00:10:16,291
Itsuki.

235
00:10:16,375 --> 00:10:20,208
[ITSUKI]
Found it! Mahiru, I found it!

236
00:10:20,291 --> 00:10:22,291
My sweet little key chain!

237
00:10:22,375 --> 00:10:24,791
[ITSUKI]
Here. Try not to lose it.

238
00:10:25,833 --> 00:10:28,041
I’m so relieved.
Thank you.

239
00:10:28,125 --> 00:10:29,750
Hey, Mahiru.

240
00:10:29,833 --> 00:10:31,916
Once we’ve grown up,
let’s stay together,

241
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,625
just like this, okay?

242
00:10:33,708 --> 00:10:35,000
Itsuki.

243
00:10:35,083 --> 00:10:36,875
No way, you actually remembered!

